{
  "stem": "19596.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 245.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even if you take an Australian non-Jew who went through the war, he's a different type of man than a fellow never been through anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Much more mature, broader outlook, more understanding of human needs and things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Cares more for people than other people do, that what my opinion is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, I do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Particular, particular to some of those Ukrainians and Poles, very bad people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- in my opinion, they even haven't changed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You've got a lot of good ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, you know, they suffer too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But those simple people, those people who have made life terrible, the kapos and the [? unterkapos ?] of those nationalities.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even after the war, what I heard from other people in Poland was terrible things happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Naturally, I feel bitterness to any-- any German who's about my age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Any German, any.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think they were all the same.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think that right there in the book, it's quite right to say that the German people are just as responsible as the SS.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not only the SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But today, it's a different generation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Three generations ago.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You never forgive those people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the people today is bending over to make peace with us and with Israel, and we should be tolerant towards this generation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pleasure, pleasure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
